text: Brought 杂菜饭，2 vege with 1 mushrooms dish cost me $4.40. Then when I taste it,super salty,don't know much how many tablespoons of salt in!!! Even mixed with white rice still very salty! Get young age Hypertension!

Worst service ever provided by the plumper size chinese aunty that brew the coffee or tea. The way she talk to customer is very rude and impolite. Such staff will only spoiled the company reputation. Your salary came from every customer that spent in this coffeeshop and your company cam success is because all this customer as well. Don't talk rude and impolite to the customer when customer didn't even offend you!!!

Please be more hygiene also to wash your hand with soap when every time you do your other task.

Blk 803 Keat Hong Close Coffeeshop

Dont buy from the wantan noodles store. Very bad attitude from the cook. Requested for lean meat and he gave me a big stare and shouted “what?!” End up with the opposite of what i requested, gave me all the fatty meat.

decided to give this 杂菜饭 a try after seeing the $2.80 promo of 1meat + 2vege.
End i was charged $3.40 for chicken n vege. Won’t try anymore after this time.

A very good location with lots of blocks in area and bus stop is right in front with 1 and only coffee shop. But Less food choice with inconsistent food quality at economical rice which beginning was good with the right chef. bad attitude staff in HK Roast. I would rather go Keat Hong Market for better food quality. Good part only lots of seats avaliable with good zi char, malay food, tender fresh and king of fried rice.
